00:11:17.140 --> 00:11:18.460 align:middle line:90%
It's control, isn't it?

00:11:18.460 --> 00:11:19.750 align:middle line:90%
>>PHILLIPS: It's power.

00:11:19.750 --> 00:11:23.260 align:middle line:84%
It's power at the
