00:11:47.810 --> 00:11:52.680 align:middle line:84%
exposures, entrapments
happen all the time.

00:11:52.680 --> 00:11:54.250 align:middle line:90%
So they're manipulating.

00:11:54.250 --> 00:11:58.950 align:middle line:84%
These people in deep state
politics, behind the scenes,

00:11:58.950 --> 00:12:00.610 align:middle line:90%
