00:12:07.600 --> 00:12:08.890 align:middle line:90%
They know what to do.

00:12:08.890 --> 00:12:11.000 align:middle line:84%
And as long as they
get the job done,

00:12:11.000 --> 00:12:13.820 align:middle line:84%
