00:14:15.470 --> 00:14:18.380 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Peter, I want to take
a look at a clip on the Bohemian

00:14:18.380 --> 00:14:18.730 align:middle line:90%
Grove.

00:14:18.730 --> 00:14:19.290 align:middle line:90%
>>PHILLIPS: OK.

00:14:19.290 --> 00:14:21.456 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: And then we'll
come back and talk about it.

00:14:21.456 --> 00:14:24.000 align:middle line:90%
Take a look at this first.

00:14:24.000 --> 00:14:27.570 align:middle line:84%
>>Located within the redwoods
of Sonoma County, California,

00:14:27.570 --> 00:14:30.950 align:middle line:84%
Bohemian Grove is the
stuff of conspiracy legend.

00:14:30.950 --> 00:14:33.560 align:middle line:84%
The Grove is owned by
the all-male Bohemian

00:14:33.560 --> 00:14:37.640 align:middle line:84%
Club, which was founded
in San Francisco in 1872.

00:14:37.640 --> 00:14:40.560 align:middle line:84%
Today it is one of the most
exclusive clubs in the United

00:14:40.560 --> 00:14:41.360 align:middle line:90%
States.

00:14:41.360 --> 00:14:44.040 align:middle line:84%
The waiting list for
membership is decades long,

00:14:44.040 --> 00:14:45.820 align:middle line:84%
and the membership
roster includes

00:14:45.820 --> 00:14:48.590 align:middle line:84%
numerous influential
men, US presidents,

00:14:48.590 --> 00:14:51.210 align:middle line:84%
foreign dignitaries,
writers like Mark Twain,

00:14:51.210 --> 00:14:53.240 align:middle line:90%
and businessmen like Henry Ford.

00:14:53.240 --> 00:14:55.450 align:middle line:84%
Each year, the members
gather with their guests

00:14:55.450 --> 00:14:58.910 align:middle line:84%
for a 16-day-long
closed door celebration.

00:14:58.910 --> 00:15:01.160 align:middle line:10%
Rumors about this
meeting run wild,

00:15:01.160 --> 00:15:03.350 align:middle line:10%
from allegations of
hedonistic partying

00:15:03.350 --> 00:15:06.970 align:middle line:10%
to outright human sacrifice
and worship of a gigantic owl

00:15:06.970 --> 00:15:07.880 align:middle line:10%
statute.

00:15:07.880 --> 00:15:09.820 align:middle line:84%
For years, members
of the public have

00:15:09.820 --> 00:15:11.610 align:middle line:84%
tried to infiltrate
this gathering

00:15:11.610 --> 00:15:13.520 align:middle line:84%
and learn what's
actually going on.

00:15:13.520 --> 00:15:14.890 align:middle line:90%
Are the rumors true?

00:15:14.890 --> 00:15:16.770 align:middle line:84%
Could the leaders
of the United States

00:15:16.770 --> 00:15:19.330 align:middle line:84%
really meet in secret
once a year for rituals

00:15:19.330 --> 00:15:20.980 align:middle line:90%
and obscure celebrations?

00:15:20.980 --> 00:15:24.190 align:middle line:84%
It seems far fetched, but
here's where it gets crazy.

00:15:24.190 --> 00:15:28.870 align:middle line:84%
It's true-- or at least some of
it, including the owl statute.

00:15:28.870 --> 00:15:31.210 align:middle line:84%
In 1989, journalist
Phillip Weiss

00:15:31.210 --> 00:15:33.220 align:middle line:90%
managed to sneak into the Grove.

00:15:33.220 --> 00:15:35.220 align:middle line:10%
In his article for
"Spy" magazine,

00:15:35.220 --> 00:15:37.300 align:middle line:10%
Weiss describes the situation.

00:15:37.300 --> 00:15:40.100 align:middle line:84%
CEOs, celebrities, and
government officials

00:15:40.100 --> 00:15:42.470 align:middle line:84%
were partying with
elaborate performances,

00:15:42.470 --> 00:15:45.470 align:middle line:84%
round-the-clock drinks,
songs, and speeches.

00:15:45.470 --> 00:15:48.370 align:middle line:10%
The opening ceremony, called
the cremation of care,

00:15:48.370 --> 00:15:50.540 align:middle line:10%
is one of the
strangest performances.

00:15:50.540 --> 00:15:52.910 align:middle line:10%
In this ceremony, people
dressed as priests

00:15:52.910 --> 00:15:55.850 align:middle line:10%
bear the crypt of a
symbolic Mr. Dull Care

00:15:55.850 --> 00:15:57.650 align:middle line:10%
to the edge of the Grove's lake.

00:15:57.650 --> 00:16:01.190 align:middle line:84%
More characters emerge at the
base of a 40-foot-tall statue

00:16:01.190 --> 00:16:02.010 align:middle line:90%
of an owl.

00:16:02.010 --> 00:16:04.570 align:middle line:84%
These characters sing
a ceremonial song,

00:16:04.570 --> 00:16:06.360 align:middle line:90%
and more spectacles occur.

00:16:06.360 --> 00:16:09.180 align:middle line:84%
Each year, the owl of
Bohemia instructs the members

00:16:09.180 --> 00:16:11.210 align:middle line:84%
to burn the crypt
of Mr. Dull Care

00:16:11.210 --> 00:16:15.250 align:middle line:84%
with the eternal
flame of fellowship.

00:16:15.250 --> 00:16:18.430 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Peter, our buddy Alex
Jones infiltrated the Bohemian

00:16:18.430 --> 00:16:20.430 align:middle line:90%
Grove many years ago.

00:16:20.430 --> 00:16:24.740 align:middle line:84%
That's a strange,
strange place, isn't it?

00:16:24.740 --> 00:16:26.480 align:middle line:90%
>>PHILLIPS: I was there.

00:16:26.480 --> 00:16:29.500 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Did you infiltrate,
or invited guest?

00:16:29.500 --> 00:16:30.970 align:middle line:84%
>>PHILLIPS: I was
an invited guest.

00:16:30.970 --> 00:16:34.140 align:middle line:84%
I did my dissertation
on the Bohemian Grove.

00:16:34.140 --> 00:16:38.200 align:middle line:84%
And a good part of the
clip, it kind of exaggerates

00:16:38.200 --> 00:16:39.000 align:middle line:90%
what they're about.

00:16:39.000 --> 00:16:40.309 align:middle line:90%
I mean, it's a big men's party.

00:16:40.309 --> 00:16:41.350 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: It is, for sure.

00:16:41.350 --> 00:16:43.516 align:middle line:84%
>>PHILLIPS: There's some
very powerful people there.

00:16:43.516 --> 00:16:44.730 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Is it a club?

00:16:44.730 --> 00:16:46.563 align:middle line:84%
>>PHILLIPS: Yeah, it's
a private men's club.

00:16:46.563 --> 00:16:48.340 align:middle line:90%
It's for men only.

00:16:48.340 --> 00:16:50.152 align:middle line:84%
They don't have
women membership.

00:16:50.152 --> 00:16:52.110 align:middle line:84%
They have a club in San
Francisco, a clubhouse.

00:16:52.110 --> 00:16:53.540 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Do you still go?

00:16:53.540 --> 00:16:55.150 align:middle line:84%
>>PHILLIPS: No, no,
I wasn't a member.

00:16:55.150 --> 00:16:56.691 align:middle line:84%
I just wrote my
dissertation on them.

00:16:56.691 --> 00:16:58.290 align:middle line:90%
I was invited as a guest.

00:16:58.290 --> 00:16:59.940 align:middle line:90%
So I you get to go to Grove.

00:16:59.940 --> 00:17:02.340 align:middle line:84%
I saw the cremation
of care ceremony.

00:17:02.340 --> 00:17:06.099 align:middle line:84%
I interviewed, literally,
hundreds of bohemians.

00:17:06.099 --> 00:17:08.829 align:middle line:90%
They are powerful people.

00:17:08.829 --> 00:17:11.170 align:middle line:84%
One out of five is
somebody very powerful

00:17:11.170 --> 00:17:14.119 align:middle line:84%
in government or a
major corporation.

00:17:14.119 --> 00:17:15.470 align:middle line:90%
They interact and play together.

00:17:15.470 --> 00:17:16.270 align:middle line:90%
They drink a lot.

00:17:16.270 --> 00:17:17.750 align:middle line:90%
They entertain each other.

00:17:17.750 --> 00:17:21.778 align:middle line:10%
The cremation of care
ceremony is a little bizarre,

00:17:21.778 --> 00:17:23.319 align:middle line:10%
because they are
dressed up in robes,

00:17:23.319 --> 00:17:25.000 align:middle line:10%
and they do burn the
skeleton of care.

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:26.430 align:middle line:10%
>>NOORY: Like "Eyes Wide Shut?"

