00:17:43.734 --> 00:17:45.950 align:middle line:90%
kind of chuckling and stuff.

00:17:45.950 --> 00:17:48.040 align:middle line:90%
But some take it very seriously.

00:17:48.040 --> 00:17:50.800 align:middle line:84%
But part of it, the seriousness
