00:17:53.010 --> 00:17:55.160 align:middle line:84%
And they can talk
with the same people.

00:17:55.160 --> 00:17:57.715 align:middle line:84%
And they have little cabins
they can stay in, and camps.

00:17:57.715 --> 00:18:01.770 align:middle line:84%
There's 120 different camps,
and every camp has a bar.

00:18:01.770 --> 00:18:03.690 align:middle line:90%
And they have lunch there.

00:18:03.690 --> 00:18:07.110 align:middle line:84%
And then there's a big dining
area where they all go.

00:18:07.110 --> 00:18:09.220 align:middle line:84%
But there's lots of
entertainment, lots of poetry,

00:18:09.220 --> 00:18:12.240 align:middle line:84%
