then a lot of conversations

00:18:12.240 --> 00:18:14.680 align:middle line:84%
about politics, and
business, and that.

00:18:14.680 --> 00:18:16.430 align:middle line:84%
They're not supposed
to do business there.

00:18:16.430 --> 00:18:19.040 align:middle line:84%
They don't per se,
