They do $35 trillion
worth of wealth.

00:30:01.990 --> 00:30:05.169 align:middle line:84%
They're the ones that are
putting advertisements out.

00:30:05.169 --> 00:30:07.210 align:middle line:84%
But they also work for
the International Monetary

00:30:07.210 --> 00:30:09.490 align:middle line:90%
Fund, the World Bank.

00:30:09.490 --> 00:30:12.950 align:middle line:84%
They do the ads for the Navy,
and the Marines, and everyone

00:30:12.950 --> 00:30:13.750 align:middle line:90%
else.

00:30:13.750 --> 00:30:18.270 align:middle line:84%
