And it came out first
during the Army-Navy game.

00:30:23.930 --> 00:30:25.260 align:middle line:10%
>>NOORY: And it was slick.

00:30:25.260 --> 00:30:26.230 align:middle line:10%
>>PHILLIPS: Very slick.

00:30:26.230 --> 00:30:28.410 align:middle line:10%
And it's this family in
the middle of the street,

00:30:28.410 --> 00:30:30.190 align:middle line:10%
and a cute little girl.

00:30:30.190 --> 00:30:32.850 align:middle line:10%
And then there's surrounded
by all the different people

00:30:32.850 --> 00:30:34.767 align:middle line:10%
in the Navy, and the
Marines, and women.

00:30:34.767 --> 00:30:36.350 align:middle line:10%
>>NOORY: And you
feel safe and secure.

00:30:36.350 --> 00:30:37.355 align:middle line:10%
>>PHILLIPS: Feel
safe and secure.

