There's nothing else about it.

00:30:41.140 --> 00:30:46.040 align:middle line:10%
It's that the national
security state is protecting us

00:30:46.040 --> 00:30:48.049 align:middle line:10%
from them, the bad people.

00:30:48.049 --> 00:30:50.340 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Well, they probably
got the idea from Goebbels

00:30:50.340 --> 00:30:52.380 align:middle line:84%
