Nice contracts, huh?

00:32:00.280 --> 00:32:01.130 align:middle line:84%
>>PHILLIPS: They're
a huge version

00:32:01.130 --> 00:32:02.950 align:middle line:84%
of-- well, a lot of
people know Blackwater,

00:32:02.950 --> 00:32:04.950 align:middle line:90%
which is now Constellis.

00:32:04.950 --> 00:32:07.842 align:middle line:84%
Triple Canopy, they
