00:32:07.842 --> 00:32:09.800 align:middle line:84%
So there's a lot of
private mercenary companies

00:32:09.800 --> 00:32:11.360 align:middle line:90%
all over the world.

00:32:11.360 --> 00:32:16.090 align:middle line:84%
In some cases, they are
the police for states,

00:32:16.090 --> 00:32:16.890 align:middle line:90%
like Honduras.

00:32:16.890 --> 00:32:19.340 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: So if they want
